My point was that I don't feel like there is anything similar to what Eamin is talking about.  Everyone has some form of utility or another.  And although Wizzies have special emphasis on nuking compared to anything else we do, we're still in the background.  We're backup, not on the front lines.  We're still not efficient.  I think this thread pretty much proves that.<br>
<br>
That's also why I said pure magical caster.  I don't consider pets &quot;pure.&quot;<br>
<br>
I mean mana =&gt; damage<br>
